00:07:21.858 --> 00:07:25.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así, puede que no aproveches</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>al máximo tu herramienta,</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:25.153 --> 00:07:27.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>lo que te deja en desventaja.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:34.745 --> 00:07:35.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Senshi!</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:35.663 --> 00:07:37.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Ahora, Laios!</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:45.506 --> 00:07:48.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Estás herida, gatita?</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:49.218 --> 00:07:51.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lamento haberte asustado.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:51.762 --> 00:07:52.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sin embargo,</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:57.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>hay formas correctas y equivocadas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de sostener una herramienta.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:57.185 --> 00:07:59.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero que pienses por qué.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:59.645 --> 00:08:02.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y por qué no deberías moverte</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mientras se deshace un hechizo.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:03.232 --> 00:08:06.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si los hechizos hubieran sido peores,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>quién sabe qué habría pasado.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:07.945 --> 00:08:10.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La comida se enfrió.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:10.531 --> 00:08:12.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La recalentaré rápido.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:14.535 --> 00:08:15.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Entonces?</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:15.453 --> 00:08:17.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué nos perseguías?</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:18.956 --> 00:08:23.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todo este tiempo estuve buscando una forma</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de romper las maldiciones en mi cuerpo.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:25.713 --> 00:08:28.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Resulta que estas maldiciones</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>fueron hechas con magia negra.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:28.841 --> 00:08:32.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero nunca pude encontrar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a alguien que pudiera usar la magia negra.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:32.887 --> 00:08:35.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hasta que me crucé con esa orejas largas.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:35.556 --> 00:08:38.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>La magia negra, digo antigua,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>puede ser de muchos tipos.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:38.309 --> 00:08:40.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Investigo cómo extraer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>energía de otra dimensión…</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:40.937 --> 00:08:41.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Basta!</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:41.854 --> 00:08:44.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sé que puedes hacerlo!</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:44.106 --> 00:08:46.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Lo has hecho antes!</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:46.734 --> 00:08:50.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¡Usaste magia negra para crear
esa espeluznante criatura mitad bestia!</i></c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:51.656 --> 00:08:54.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y todos se pasean por esta mazmorra</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:55.076 --> 00:08:56.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>para romper la maldición de esa mujer.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:56.786 --> 00:08:59.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Eso significa que sabes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cómo romper maldiciones!</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:59.997 --> 00:09:02.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En ese caso,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡puedes liberarme a mí también!</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:06.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Deshazte del alma</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de esta bestia que me posee!</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:09.090 --> 00:09:10.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo siento.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:10.716 --> 00:09:13.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedo hacer nada al respecto.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:14.095 --> 00:09:15.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:15.763 --> 00:09:18.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hay mucho que no sabemos del alma,</i></c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:18.724 --> 00:09:20.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>pero suele compararse con un huevo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:21.185 --> 00:09:24.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Normalmente, está
dentro de una cáscara que llamamos carne,</i></c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:24.230 --> 00:09:26.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>pero, una vez que la carne se rompe,
las entrañas salen</i></c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:26.899 --> 00:09:28.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>y no se pueden volver a poner.</i></c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:29.777 --> 00:09:31.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Este calabozo está bajo un hechizo</i></c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:31.654 --> 00:09:34.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>que forma una membrana dura
bajo la cáscara,</i></c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:34.949 --> 00:09:37.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>que mantiene el alma dentro
aunque el cuerpo esté dañado.</i></c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:38.077 --> 00:09:43.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En este momento, Falin y tú tienen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dos huevos dentro de una cáscara.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:44.542 --> 00:09:46.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y, una vez mezclados,</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:46.711 --> 00:09:48.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>esas almas nunca volverán</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a su forma original.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:50.047 --> 00:09:53.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Lo sabía, pero oírlo así
te afecta de otra manera.</i></c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:54.302 --> 00:09:55.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:55.845 --> 00:10:00.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si es así, ¿por qué siguen con su viaje?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:02.935 --> 00:10:06.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una razón es que no podemos dejar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que mi hermana se descontrole.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:06.522 --> 00:10:09.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Podría matar al próximo aventurero</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con el que se cruce.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:09.859 --> 00:10:11.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O hacer que la maten.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:10:11.944 --> 00:10:13.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Queremos hacer algo antes de que eso pase.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:14.405 --> 00:10:17.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y, si regresamos a la superficie ahora,</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:17.199 --> 00:10:19.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>nos arrestarán por usar magia negra.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:19.452 --> 00:10:22.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puede que Shuro le cuente</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>al señor de la isla sobre este incidente.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:23.456 --> 00:10:24.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero…</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:25.333 --> 00:10:28.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Significa que estoy atrapada así?</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:28.210 --> 00:10:30.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No, escúchame!</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:30.171 --> 00:10:34.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sé que puede sonar raro,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero me alegra haberte conocido.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:34.091 --> 00:10:36.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>No sé con qué clase</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de monstruo estás mezclada,</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:36.427 --> 00:10:38.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero te comportas como un humano.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:38.929 --> 00:10:40.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y tampoco buscas sangre.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:41.349 --> 00:10:44.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así que quizá hasta Falin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una vez que se libere del calabozo,</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:45.019 --> 00:10:47.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pueda recuperar su verdadero ser.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:48.147 --> 00:10:51.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Darme cuenta de eso</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:51.359 --> 00:10:53.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>me hace muy feliz ahora.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:54.236 --> 00:10:55.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toma.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:55.863 --> 00:10:59.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizá las cosas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no salieron como esperabas,</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:01.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero ¿por qué no verlo de modo positivo,</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:01.160 --> 00:11:02.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>como si fuera obra del destino?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:03.371 --> 00:11:05.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El señor de la mazmorra</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:05.122 --> 00:11:08.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>es mucho más hábil</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con la magia antigua que yo.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:08.626 --> 00:11:13.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Podría saber cómo separar las almas.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:13.881 --> 00:11:14.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:17.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Intentan reclutarme?</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:17.134 --> 00:11:20.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como sea, no puedes volver</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a la superficie sola.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:20.596 --> 00:11:23.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Te llamabas Asebi o algo así?</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:23.265 --> 00:11:25.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así me conocen.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:25.309 --> 00:11:26.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entonces…</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:26.310 --> 00:11:27.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Izutsumi.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:27.395 --> 00:11:29.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me llamo Izutsumi.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:29.355 --> 00:11:30.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo olviden.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:41.158 --> 00:11:44.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Laios, ¿cuánto tiempo más vas a vivir así?</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:45.037 --> 00:11:45.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Padre.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:45.955 --> 00:11:48.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es hora de que vivas una vida decente.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:48.165 --> 00:11:51.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te dejé salir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para que fueras a matar dragones.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:11:52.044 --> 00:11:53.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Regresa a la aldea!</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:11:54.171 --> 00:11:55.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero Falin sigue…</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:11:55.506 --> 00:11:57.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Olvídate de ella.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:11:57.800 --> 00:12:01.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿De verdad crees</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que alguien como tú puede salir</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:01.804 --> 00:12:04.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>cuando huiste de la escuela</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y del ejército porque no encajabas?</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:05.808 --> 00:12:08.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ni siquiera sabes explorar la mazmorra.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:08.811 --> 00:12:10.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como cuando eras rascador de oro,</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:10.729 --> 00:12:13.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>tus camaradas te engañarán</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y se llevarán el crédito de tus logros.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:14.316 --> 00:12:16.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Porque no tienes idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de cómo leer a la gente.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:17.319 --> 00:12:18.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A mí me pasó lo mismo.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:19.071 --> 00:12:22.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creías que éramos buenos amigos,</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:22.241 --> 00:12:23.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero yo siempre odié…</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:24.034 --> 00:12:24.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Puedes olvidarlo?</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:25.077 --> 00:12:26.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya lo hablamos.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:26.745 --> 00:12:28.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:28.456 --> 00:12:30.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Qué hacen mis padres aquí?</i></c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:30.958 --> 00:12:33.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hace más de una década que no los veo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:33.210 --> 00:12:35.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Y dónde estoy?</i></c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:35.087 --> 00:12:36.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Qué estaba haciendo?</i></c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:36.714 --> 00:12:38.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Creo que estaba…</i></c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:41.719 --> 00:12:43.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
