00:18:04.625 --> 00:18:08.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>No, quiere que nos sintamos
ansiosos y asustados.</i></c.bg_transparent>

329
00:18:08.212 --> 00:18:10.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Debo levantarle el ánimo a Marcille.</i></c.bg_transparent>

330
00:18:10.130 --> 00:18:11.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No te preocupes!</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:18:11.381 --> 00:18:13.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Puedes usar magia!</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:18:13.592 --> 00:18:16.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Puedes acabar con esa cosa tú sola!</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:18:17.012 --> 00:18:18.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Magia?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:18:23.393 --> 00:18:25.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>El lugar está cada vez más inestable.</i></c.bg_transparent>

335
00:18:25.437 --> 00:18:27.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Dije algo malo?</i></c.bg_transparent>

336
00:18:27.272 --> 00:18:28.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando…</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:18:28.899 --> 00:18:32.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando intenté usar magia para vencerlo,</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:18:32.778 --> 00:18:35.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ella terminó así.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:18:36.698 --> 00:18:37.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ella?</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:18:37.783 --> 00:18:40.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera, ¿esa es Falin?</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:18:40.285 --> 00:18:41.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ahora lo entiendo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

342
00:18:42.037 --> 00:18:44.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Marcille se siente culpable
por la transformación de Falin</i></c.bg_transparent>

343
00:18:44.164 --> 00:18:46.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>debido a su magia de resurrección.</i></c.bg_transparent>

344
00:18:46.125 --> 00:18:48.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Si intentó derrotar a esa cosa, significa…</i></c.bg_transparent>

345
00:18:48.794 --> 00:18:51.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¡que Marcille le teme a la muerte!</i></c.bg_transparent>

346
00:18:51.797 --> 00:18:53.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Está regresando!</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:18:54.174 --> 00:18:56.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Huir no resolverá nada.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:18:56.677 --> 00:18:58.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tienes que enfrentarlo.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:18:58.637 --> 00:18:59.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:18:59.680 --> 00:19:02.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te preocupes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡No tienes nada que temer!</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:19:03.433 --> 00:19:05.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En la mazmorra,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aunque mueras, puedes revivir.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:19:05.936 --> 00:19:09.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Incluso Falin está viva</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gracias a tu magia de resurrección.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:19:09.439 --> 00:19:11.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y estás acostumbrada a ver cadáveres, ¿no?</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:19:11.733 --> 00:19:13.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:19:18.657 --> 00:19:20.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Me está jalando!</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:19:20.200 --> 00:19:21.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No!</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:19:21.451 --> 00:19:23.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Solo me está jalando a mí!</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:19:23.203 --> 00:19:24.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Toma mi mano!</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:19:28.083 --> 00:19:29.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>No es veneno.</i></c.bg_transparent>

360
00:19:29.459 --> 00:19:32.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Envejezco a un ritmo increíble.</i></c.bg_transparent>

361
00:19:33.088 --> 00:19:34.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera un minuto, Marcille.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:19:34.715 --> 00:19:35.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debo recuperar el aliento.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:19:36.967 --> 00:19:38.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Algo no está bien.</i></c.bg_transparent>

364
00:19:38.594 --> 00:19:41.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Hay una criatura capaz de esto?</i></c.bg_transparent>

365
00:19:41.346 --> 00:19:43.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tal vez ni siquiera sea una criatura.</i></c.bg_transparent>

366
00:19:43.807 --> 00:19:46.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tampoco vendrás conmigo?</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:19:46.476 --> 00:19:49.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, puedo volver a correr</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>después de descansar un poco.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:19:49.438 --> 00:19:50.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Mientes!</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:19:50.355 --> 00:19:54.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todos los que corrieron conmigo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>se rindieron, y esa cosa se los tragó.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:19:54.943 --> 00:19:58.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Papá, Pipi, Falin, todos!</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:19:58.447 --> 00:20:01.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por eso estudié mucha magia.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:20:01.783 --> 00:20:05.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero, si eso es</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lo que convirtió a Falin en esto,</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:20:05.120 --> 00:20:07.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no sé qué hacer.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:20:08.749 --> 00:20:11.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tu padre murió joven?</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:20:12.336 --> 00:20:15.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En el funeral de papá, mamá me dijo</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:20:16.006 --> 00:20:19.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>que corro más rápido que los demás.</i></c.bg_transparent>

377
00:20:19.551 --> 00:20:23.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Que tendría que ver irse a mucha gente.</i></c.bg_transparent>

378
00:20:24.014 --> 00:20:26.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por cierto, ¿Pipi es pariente tuyo?</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:20:26.683 --> 00:20:27.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pipi es un pájaro.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:20:27.768 --> 00:20:28.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ya veo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

381
00:20:29.519 --> 00:20:32.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Marcille no le teme a la muerte.</i></c.bg_transparent>

382
00:20:32.689 --> 00:20:36.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Le preocupa que sus seres queridos
mueran antes que ella.</i></c.bg_transparent>

383
00:20:42.866 --> 00:20:44.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marcille, ¡cálmate!</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:20:44.284 --> 00:20:47.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si tienes miedo, eso solo la fortalecerá.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:20:47.287 --> 00:20:49.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero ¿qué se supone que haga?</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:20:49.957 --> 00:20:51.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No puedo hacer nada!</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:20:51.166 --> 00:20:52.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No, tú puedes!</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:20:52.793 --> 00:20:55.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Eres increíble, Marcille!</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:20:55.295 --> 00:20:57.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Mira todos estos libros!</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:20:57.798 --> 00:21:00.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No había nada así en mi sueño!</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:21:00.801 --> 00:21:03.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Has estado trabajando</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>incansablemente todo este tiempo!</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:21:03.553 --> 00:21:06.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te desanimes. ¡Ten fe en ti misma!</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:21:06.556 --> 00:21:08.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Tú puedes, Marcille!</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:21:08.433 --> 00:21:10.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No, levántate!</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:21:10.435 --> 00:21:11.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Tenemos que correr!</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:21:11.895 --> 00:21:12.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y, además,</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:21:13.063 --> 00:21:15.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡mi magia no está desarrollada</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por completo!</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:21:15.816 --> 00:21:18.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Si tuviera el mismo libro que él,</i></c.bg_transparent>

399
00:21:18.860 --> 00:21:21.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>podría usar la magia
con más eficacia, pero…</i></c.bg_transparent>

400
00:21:21.613 --> 00:21:23.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Entonces, deséalo!</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:21:23.949 --> 00:21:26.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si lo deseas con fuerza,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡puedes lograr lo que sea!</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:21:26.702 --> 00:21:29.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No tengas miedo!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡Puedes hacerlo mejor la próxima vez!</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:21:29.830 --> 00:21:31.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No te rindas!</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:21:31.957 --> 00:21:34.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No!</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:21:34.710 --> 00:21:36.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No!</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:21:44.594 --> 00:21:46.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Eso es, Marcille!</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:21:46.430 --> 00:21:47.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Hazlo!</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:21:58.025 --> 00:22:01.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Así es como lo usas?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:22:05.073 --> 00:22:06.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estás despierto.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:22:06.408 --> 00:22:08.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ambos gruñían mientras dormían.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:22:08.327 --> 00:22:09.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Estás bien?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:22:09.453 --> 00:22:11.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo recuerdo.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:22:11.955 --> 00:22:14.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero fue un sueño agotador.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:22:19.212 --> 00:22:20.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Se vuelve a dormir!</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:22:20.297 --> 00:22:22.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No! ¡Despierta, Marcille!</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:22:23.800 --> 00:22:24.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Mi sueño?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:22:25.344 --> 00:22:26.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No recuerdo mucho.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:29.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero creo que fue divertido.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:22:29.681 --> 00:22:31.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece que funcionó.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:22:31.391 --> 00:22:32.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Pasó algo?</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:22:32.976 --> 00:22:34.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pásame tu almohada.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:22:34.603 --> 00:22:35.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:22:38.774 --> 00:22:39.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué es eso?</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:22:39.691 --> 00:22:41.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pesadillas.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:22:41.109 --> 00:22:44.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se esconden en las almohadas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y provocan sueños malos.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:22:45.363 --> 00:22:47.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay muchas.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:22:47.657 --> 00:22:49.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deben haber estado anidando</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en tu almohada.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:22:49.951 --> 00:22:50.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No puede ser!</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:22:50.869 --> 00:22:52.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senshi, ¿son comestibles?</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:22:52.746 --> 00:22:54.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Siempre me intrigó su sabor.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:22:54.831 --> 00:22:56.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, claro.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Primero, limpiémoslas.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:23:00.754 --> 00:23:03.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si las remojas en agua caliente así…</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:23:04.257 --> 00:23:07.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Las pesadillas,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>también conocidas como </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>shen,</i></c.bg_transparent>

435
00:23:07.219 --> 00:23:09.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>están relacionadas con los dragones.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:23:09.096 --> 00:23:11.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si miras de cerca,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>son parecidas a los dragones.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:23:11.139 --> 00:23:12.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Es una broma?</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:23:12.516 --> 00:23:16.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Colocas las pesadillas
en mantequilla derretida,</i></c.bg_transparent>

439
00:23:16.353 --> 00:23:18.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
